<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">How to use the Wordle Solver</h2>



<p>Wordle Solver is designed to emulate Wordle rules, making it easy for th=
e user to instantly generate all potential solutions. Just place letters fr=
om your Wordle game in the following fields:</p>



<ol class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><strong><mark style=3D"background-color:#6ca965" class=3D"has-inline-co=
lor">=E2=80=9CCorrect letters=E2=80=9D</mark></strong> field: corresponding=
 with Wordle=E2=80=99s green letters, place correctly guessed letters from =
your Wordle game in this field, in their respective positions.<br></li>



<li><strong><mark style=3D"background-color:#c8b653;color:#000000" class=3D=
"has-inline-color">=E2=80=9CMisplaced letters=E2=80=9D</mark></strong> fiel=
d: analogous to Wordle=E2=80=99s yellow letters, these fields identify lett=
ers contained in the Wordle answer that are not in the correct position. Th=
e tool will then search for words containing yellow letters in all other po=
sitions.
<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li>Have in mind that the yellow fields are position-based. For example, if=
 you place the letter E in the second position, the tool will find all word=
s that contain the letter E in the first, third, fourth, and fifth position=
s.</li>



<li>Each Wordle guess should be placed in its own row. The tool allows you =
to add or remove yellow rows accordingly.<br></li>
</ul>
</li>



<li><strong><mark style=3D"background-color:#787c7f" class=3D"has-inline-co=
lor">=E2=80=9CLetters NOT in the word=E2=80=9D</mark></strong>: whenever Wo=
rdle marks your letter grey, place it in this field. The tool will then exc=
lude all the words containing this letter as a potential Wordle solution.</=
li>
</ol>



<p>Once you=E2=80=99ve placed all the letters in their respective fields an=
d positions, hit the Submit button. The tool will generate all potential Wo=
rdle solutions, ordered alphabetically.</p>



